// DesignHistoryDropdown
// Version history dropdown for the design editor. Fetches version content on
// selection and calls onVersionSelect.

FUNCTION formatTimestamp(ts) -> string
  Today: returns time only (HH:MM).
  Yesterday: returns "Yesterday HH:MM".
  Within 7 days: returns "DayName HH:MM".
  Older: returns "Mon DD, HH:MM".

---

FUNCTION DesignHistoryDropdown(history, onVersionSelect, onClose) -> JSX  EXPORT
  Renders a dropdown list of history entries with formatted timestamps.
  Clicking an entry fetches the version content via getVersionAt, then calls
  onVersionSelect(content) if non-null. Closes dropdown.
  Closes on click outside. Disabled when history is empty.

---

FUNCTION handleItemClick(version) -> void
  Fetches version content. Calls onVersionSelect if content is non-null. Closes.
